.Dd March 04, 2026
.Dt DIRECTOR 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm appjail-director
.Nd Define and run multi-jail environments with AppJail
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
.Cm up
.Op Fl Fl json
.Op Fl Fl overwrite
.Op Fl Fl quiet
.Op Fl Fl file Ar file
.Op Fl Fl project Ar name
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
.Cm down
.Op Fl Fl ignore-failed
.Op Fl Fl ignore-services
.Op Fl Fl json
.Op Fl Fl quiet
.Op Fl Fl destroy
.Op Fl Fl project Ar name
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
.Cm ls
.Op Fl Fl state Ar state
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
.Cm info
.Op Fl Fl project Ar name
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
.Cm describe
.Op Fl Fl project Ar name
.Nm
.Op Fl Fl config Ar file
.Op Fl Fl env-file Ar file
